      "solution": "def count_divisors(n):\n    count = 0\n    i = 1\n    while i * i <= n:\n        if n % i == 0:\n            if i * i == n:\n                count += 1\n            else:\n                count += 2\n        i += 1\n    return count\n\nn = int(input())\nprint(count_divisors(n))",
